<item>
            <title>[HBASE-5961] New standard HBase code formatter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5961</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is currently no good way of passing out the formmatter currently the &apos;standard&apos; in HBase. The standard Apache formatter is actually not very close to what we are considering &apos;good&apos;/&apos;pretty&apos; code. Further, its not trivial to get a good formatter setup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Proposing two things: &lt;br/&gt;
1) Adding a formmatter to the dev tools and calling out the formmatter usage in the docs&lt;br/&gt;
2) Move to a &apos;better&apos; formmatter that is not the standard apache formmatter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
