                            <comment id="13270739" author="stack" created="Tue, 8 May 2012 19:21:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We need to check this in or do we just have the reference guide refer to this issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13270803" author="jesse_yates" created="Tue, 8 May 2012 20:40:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Was thinking this could be checked in, so we have a single source of truth. In the future, if people want to update it, they just modify the file, rather than be pointed to a jira which could end up holding a ton of versions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
