                            <comment id="13462401" author="jesse_yates" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2012 03:23:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=saint.ack%40gmail.com&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;saint.ack@gmail.com&quot;&gt;Stack&lt;/a&gt; sounds good! And maybe update the book when you commit with info about where to find the formatter/template?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13462851" author="cody.marcel@gmail.com" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2012 15:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Nice!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13463047" author="stack" created="Tue, 25 Sep 2012 17:58:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed this formatter under dev-support and I added how to install doc from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3678&quot; title=&quot;Add Eclipse-based Apache Formatter to HBase Wiki&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-3678&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-3678&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
